quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  29,46,"Wota on weeñir yimɓe defte ɓen si wonaa e no ɓuri e moƴƴirde, si wonaa hara ko ɓen tooñɓe e maɓɓe. Mbi'on: "Min ngooŋɗinii nden njippinaande e amen e ɗen njippinaaɗe e mon. Deweteeɗo amen On e deweteeɗo mon On ko gooto, menen non, ko Min jebbilanii ɓe Mo"."
  29,47,"Ko wano non Min njippiniri e maaɗa Deftere nden. Ɓeen ɓe Min ngokki Deftere nden, heɓe mgooŋɗini nde. Hino e maɓɓe on gooŋɗinɗo nde. Yeddataa Aayeeje Amen ɗen, si wonaa heeferɓe ɓen."
  29,48,"A wonaano haɗa janngatnoo deftere ado mayre, a winndirtaano ñaamo maa ngon. Harayno, bonnooɓe ɓen cikkittono."
  29,49,"Si ko woni, ko nde Aayeeje ɓannguɗe e ɓerɗe ɓen okkaaɓe ganndal. Yeddataa aayeeje Amen ɗen, si wonaa tooñɓe ɓeen."
  29,50,"Ɓe mb'i: "Hanno jippinee e makko Ma'andeeji immorde ka Joomi makko?" Maaku: "aayaaji ko joomam addata, anndee min, ko mi jeertinoowo ɓannguɗo"."
  29,51,"Kere yonaani ɓe won'de Min njippinii e maaɗa deftere nden hende janngee e maɓɓe? Wonii e ɗuum, yurmeende e waaju wonan'de yimɓe gooŋɗinooɓe."
  29,52,"Maaku: "Alla yonii hakkunde am e mooɗon seedee Hino anndi ko woni kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Ɓen non gooŋɗimɓe meere nden ɓe yeddi Alla, ko ɓen ngoni oni sooyɓe ɓen."